These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: plum, broccoli, carrot
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, fisherman, dancer
1. the person eating plum is in an even position##4
2. the mechanic is on the left or right of the dancer##3
3. the mechanic is the person eating broccoli##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the far left##1
5. the fisherman is the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | carrot | plum | broccoli |
| Job    | fisherman    | dancer | mechanic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, sudoku, magic-tricks
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, helicopter, train
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | sudoku | magic-tricks | reading |
| Transport   | train    | helicopter     | car        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, writing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, d&b, rock
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | writing     | hiking | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | reggae     | rock  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary, family
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, baseball, volleyball
1. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | documentary  | martial-arts  |
| Sport         | snowboarding  | baseball | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, singing, card-games
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, british, indian
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the turkish##2
2. the person who's hobby is singing is in an odd position##4
3. the indian is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks   | card-games | singing    |
| Nationality   | british | indian     | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, sudoku, hiking
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, snowboarding, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | sudoku | hiking | cooking   |
| Sport   | surfing     | rowing    | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, time-travel, musical
3 different pets are kept: snake, goldfish, frog
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is between the owner of the frog and the person watching musical movies##2
3. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | romance | time-travel |
| Pet           | goldfish         | snake         | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: radish, kiwi, papaya
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person eating radish##2
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | kiwi | papaya | radish |
| Pet    | hedgehog    | dog | guinea-pig     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, reggae, trance
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, badminton, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | reggae  | r&b  |
| Sport         | volleyball | badminton | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, sprite
There 3 different types of food: papaya, carrot, zucchini
1. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person eating zucchini is in an even position##4
3. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | sprite      | water |
| Food       | carrot | zucchini | papaya   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker, chef
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, airplane, car
1. the chef is on the right of the dressmaker##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the designer##1
3. the person driving the car is the chef##1
4. the chef is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | dressmaker | chef | designer |
| Transport   | airplane | car   | jet-ski |

