.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, indian, russian
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, train, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the italian is the person driving the boat##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the indian##3
4. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | russian | indian | italian |
| Transport     | train     | helicopter   | boat        |

