.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, indonesian, brazilian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, biathlon, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the brazilian##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is the indonesian##1
3. the brazilian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
