.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, magic-tricks
3 different pets are kept: turtle, mouse, guinea-pig
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the owner of the mouse##2
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the mouse is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | dancing | magic-tricks | card-games |
| Pet     | turtle    | guinea-pig  | mouse   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, crime, animation
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, rock, funk
1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
2. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of techno##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
4. the person watching animation movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | animation     | crime |
| Music-Genre   | rock | techno | funk    |

