.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, card-games, fishing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, indie, blues
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | fishing | woodworking   | card-games |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | d&b | blues      |

