.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, sprite
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, mexican, british
1. the british is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | water | lemonade | sprite |
| Nationality   | mexican   | british          | colombian |

