.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, frog, hedgehog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, volleyball, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | frog  | hedgehog   | cat |
| Sport   | snowboarding | volleyball | weightlifting       |

 